data.description: One-of-a-kind in Spanish Fort! This beautiful one level farmhouse is on 4.8 gorgeous acres with a pasture area for sports or horses and a serene backyard with an inground gunite pool overlooking a small creek. This home has features galore- open floor plan with split brick & hardwood floors, crown molding, recessed lighting, large bedrooms, screened-in porch, tons of storage & much more! Separate entrance makes it possible to have a mother-in-law suite. Talk about location, this property is just minutes from the Eastern Shore Centre in Spanish Fort and I-10.
